119
00:14:16,070 --> 00:14:17,050
 Your Eminence Goffredo, may I?

120
00:14:17,890 --> 00:14:18,890
 No!

121
00:14:18,930 --> 00:14:20,560
 See you later.

122
00:14:19,900 --> 00:14:22,400
 You're welcome. See you later, Your Eminence.

123
