He said some were chosen to be shepherds
and others to manage.

135
00:15:18,820 --> 00:15:21,720
Apparently I&#39;ve been selected for management.

136
00:15:23,020 --> 00:15:26,030
He told me about your crisis of faith.

137
00:15:27,790 --> 00:15:33,570
But you should know
that he had doubts too.

138
00:15:33,600 --> 00:15:36,200
Did the Pope have doubts about God?

139
00:15:36,240 --> 00:15:38,240
no.

140
