What he has lost faith in is the church.

142
00:15:43,880 --> 00:15:46,980
Father Wozniak?

143
00:15:47,010 --> 00:15:50,350
In the name of the Father, the Son and the Holy Spirit.

144
00:15:50,380 --> 00:15:51,990
- My last confession was four weeks ago. 
- &quot;Yanush.&quot;

