00:15:57,820 --> 00:16:00,060
Have you been drinking?

148
00:16:01,800 --> 00:16:03,960
What&#39;s worrying you? Tell me.

149
00:16:04,930 --> 00:16:07,100
I should have come to you before.

150
00:16:08,030 --> 00:16:09,900
But I promised not to say anything.

151
00:16:09,940 --> 00:16:13,040
- Who did you promise to? 
- Cardinal Tremblay.

152
00:16:13,070 --> 00:16:14,940
&quot;Yanush,&quot; the doors will close soon and you will have to leave.

153
00:16:14,970 --> 00:16:18,310
If you promised Cardinal Tremblay, then perhaps it is not right that...

154
00:16:18,350 --> 00:16:20,110
The day the Pope died,

