The last person he had an official appointment with was Cardinal Tremblay.

156
00:16:24,420 --> 00:16:26,390
Yes, I know that.
It&#39;s on the official timeline.

157
00:16:26,420 --> 00:16:29,720
The Pope excommunicated him at that meeting.

