Forgive me, but I only started hearing the rumors in the last few days.

165
00:16:51,250 --> 00:16:54,250
- Any rumors?
- That he might be elected pope.

166
00:16:54,280 --> 00:16:57,720
And you think it&#39;s your duty to prevent that, right?

167
00:16:57,750 --> 00:17:01,820
I don&#39;t know what my duty is anymore.

168
00:17:14,170 --> 00:17:16,400
Were you present at the meeting?

169
00:17:16,440 --> 00:17:18,000
No, your excellency.

170
00:17:18,040 --> 00:17:20,440
The Pope told me
after the meeting was over,

171
00:17:20,470 --> 00:17:22,140
When we had dinner.

172
00:17:22,180 --> 00:17:26,810
Shall I tell you why Eminence Tremblay was fired?

173
00:17:26,850 --> 00:17:28,680
no.

