Which they kept secret at the request of the Pope.

204
00:20:04,200 --> 00:20:06,970
Do you think he forged the letter?

205
00:20:07,010 --> 00:20:09,380
Where is he now?

206
00:20:11,210 --> 00:20:13,050
Cardinal in Afghanistan?

207
00:20:13,080 --> 00:20:14,620
This is ridiculous.

208
00:20:14,650 --> 00:20:16,320
How many Catholics are there in Afghanistan?

209
00:20:16,350 --> 00:20:18,420
He was the head of the Catholic mission there.

210
00:20:18,450 --> 00:20:20,990
Until he was promoted.

211
00:20:21,020 --> 00:20:23,190
But how do we ensure his safety?

212
00:20:23,220 --> 00:20:26,590
This is probably why the Pope wanted to keep his promotion a secret.

