Well, his status is not a secret anymore.

214
00:20:29,900 --> 00:20:32,600
I don&#39;t think we have a choice but to acknowledge it.

215
00:20:32,630 --> 00:20:35,100
Hold on, Thomas.

216
00:20:37,070 --> 00:20:39,470
Are we sure that the Pope

